資訊服務機構管理



資訊服務機構管理研究 
  
國立臺灣師範大學圖書資訊學研究所在職進修碩士學位班 
  
 Syllabus 

課程目標 
本 課程希望透過各種管理理論與實務的探討，提供圖書資訊機構管理者與從業人員，在面對實際問題時的解決方式。資料的研讀與同儕之間的討論，將是本課程的重點，同學可以從課堂分享他人經驗和想法 。 
  
教科書 
Stueart, R. D. and Moran, B. B. (2002). Library and information center management . 6 th ed. Greenwood Village , CO : Libraries Unlimited. 
  
參考書目 : 
Brenfeld, B. A. (2004). “ Developing a t eam m anagement s tructure in a p ublic l ibrary ”. Library Trends 53 (1), 112-128. 
Deiss, K. J. (2004). “ Innovation and s trategy: Risk and c hoice in s haping u ser- c entered l ibraries” . Library Trends 53 (1), 17-32. 
Deiss, K . & Giesecke , J. (1999). "From h ere to t here : Moving to the f uture through s cenario planning. Library Administration & Management 13 (2):99-104 
Edwards, R . L., Yankey, J . A. & Altper, M . A. (1998). Skills for effective management of nonprofit organizations . Washington , D.C. : NASW Press 
Evans, W. & Ward, B. R.(2000). Management basics for information professionals. New York : Neal-Schuman.  
Honea, S.M. (2000).”The Impact of p rofessionalism on l ibrary administration.” Journal of Library Administration, 31 :1 
